{"tid":991641,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇試過比屋企人叫你去做練馬師？","createTime":"2019-01-22T13:49:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-23T00:34:55.000Z","uid":38386,"like":46,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"7e891c8f3130fcb4b731aff87cc7ffd829e80085","tid":991641,"uid":38386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T13:49:12.000Z","msg":"細細個嗰陣阿爺逢係賽馬日必賭<br />\n<br />\n賭到80幾歲都唔厭<br />\n<br />\n仲記得有晚無端端比個新聞專欄我睇好似訪問莫雷拉之類<br />\n<br />\n講到佢贏左馬有幾多獎金搵到幾咁多錢<br />\n<br />\n於是就叫阿孫仔我不如試下去學騎馬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n嗰時仲心諗阿爺你都cls 賭馬賭上癮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n可惜而家大個左識賭馬但冇得再同阿爺一齊睇跑馬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲等我以前成日心入面屌鳩佢掛住睇馬阻住我睇電影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbaeae65388b4127f7c4f53d836f895a551b5f03","tid":991641,"uid":208348,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T13:52:07.000Z","msg":"唔好咁傷心了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50688a76c72c5eac5ee1a5783be96c774e6844fc","tid":991641,"uid":41157,"like":67,"dislike":0,"score":67,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T13:54:26.000Z","msg":"莫雷拉嚟左香港都係三幾年姐<br />\n講咩細過大過姐<br />\n講到好似想當年咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c28bb23a966d3cb71360363a209a217e01c83a2","tid":991641,"uid":80456,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"50688a76c72c5eac5ee1a5783be96c774e6844fc","tid":991641,"uid":41157,"like":67,"dislike":0,"score":67,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T13:54:26.000Z","msg":"莫雷拉嚟左香港都係三幾年姐<br />\n講咩細過大過姐<br />\n講到好似想當年咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T1